en-US.title: St. John's Community Health, Portland
en-US.description: St. John's Community Health provides comprehensive health services to the transgender community in Portland. Services include medical and mental health services, substance use services, a transgender health program, and various patient programs. This health center serves uninsured and underinsured populations ensuring health equity for everyone, including the transgender community.

address: 808 W 58th St, Los Angeles, CA 90037, USA
